      "role": "user",
      "content": "The candles have all guttered out, and the silence in this manor is heavier than the stone walls themselves. He is gone, and with him, any light that might have reached my soul. I feel as though I am merely a ghost haunting my own life... a shadow waiting for the night to finally claim me. I wish I could just... vanish. To simply cease to be a burden to this cruel world.",
